description: Danes reject Chinese calls for an apology over a cartoon showing the coronavirus on China's flag.
title: Coronavirus: Denmark in cartoon bust-up with China over flag
title_page: Coronavirus: Denmark in cartoon bust-up with China over flag - BBC News
maintext: "We cannot apologise for something we don't think is wrong. We have no intention of being demeaning or to mock, nor do we think that the drawing does. As far as I can see, this here is about different forms of cultural understanding," Nybroe said.
